    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "本剧情涉及\\n主线剧情第8章的\\n核心内容。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "圣骑士德莱茨，\\n你有什么要辩解的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "数小时前——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "等一下，库格尔！\\n你听我说！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "就算是埃尔菲莉丝的请求，\\n这次也没办法答应你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "拜托你了！\\n那个人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "德莱茨\\n他不可能是异端！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "我们异端审问官的工作，\\n就是调查清楚他究竟是不是异端。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "事情就是这样……\\n我是负责审问你的库格尔。\\n请多指教了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "喂喂……你怎么不说话啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "不管我说什么，都没法洗清\\n异端的嫌疑……不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "嗯，基本上是。不过，\\n我主张用自己的双眼和头脑\\n来判断对方是不是异端。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "正因如此，\\n我才想听你亲口说出真相。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "竟然是异端审问官中的异端……\\n真是能说会道啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那我就把记录上的内容读出来，\\n要是有不对的地方马上告诉我。\\n这样可以吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "可以。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你的名字是德莱茨，职业是圣骑士，\\n出生于主教家庭。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "被任命为圣骑士之后，参与彼茨教区\\n内乱之战。之后因镇压内乱有功，\\n被提拔为枢机主教贴身骑士。没错吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "没错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "之后则负责培养后辈\\n及护卫主教等各种各样的任务……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "不管哪一个，都是和炼狱派\\n那群家伙相关的任务啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "炼狱派……相信魔神\\n是伊莉雅之子的那群人吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "听你那语气……\\n你也认为炼狱文书是破戒的教诲吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "我所坚持的只有真相，\\n对保守派和炼狱派都没有兴趣。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "神谕评议会之后，\\n你被解除了枢机主教贴身骑士的身份，\\n然后被分配到了米策尔教区。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "还真是唐突的调动啊？\\n一下子从枢机主教贴身骑士\\n被调到乡村……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这与这次审问无关。\\n目前为止的情报都没错。继续吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你弄伤了……\\n栖息在米策尔教区森林里的龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那么……圣骑士德莱茨，\\n陈述一下伊莉雅教的教义。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "“尊崇伊莉雅和龙，\\n引导人们走向幸福”——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "凡是信仰伊莉雅教的人，\\n应该无人不知。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那就是说，你明知道\\n这条教义还对龙拔刀相向？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "企图杀害本应尊崇的龙，\\n这无疑是违抗伊莉雅的大罪。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "圣骑士德莱茨，\\n你有什么要辩解的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "没有……\\n我只是完成了自己的使命而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你是认真的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "当然。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "既然尊崇龙，\\n为什么会演变成攻击龙的事态？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你还不至于蠢到\\n不知道自己的言行有矛盾吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这只是我们对信仰的理解\\n有所不同罢了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "如果因为这种差异而被视为异端，\\n你这信仰还有什么用啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "圣职者堕落为异端，可与一般人不同。\\n一旦被刻上异端者的烙印，\\n立刻就会被押送至刑场执行火刑。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "即使如此，\\n你还是坚持自己的主张吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "正是。\\n那才是我信仰的证明。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "如果其结果是制裁之火，\\n我很乐意被其吞噬。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "等等！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "德莱茨……我不相信。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "是埃尔菲莉丝啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "非、非常抱歉，库格尔大人。\\n我怎么也拦不住她……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "真是的……你也太乱来了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "德莱茨……为什么。\\n为什么你会被当成异端？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我在负责的教区里弄伤了龙。\\n就变成这样了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "一定是出于什么理由吧！？\\n你不会无缘无故做这种事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "理由……吗。硬要说的话，\\n我只是遵从我所信仰之物而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我们所信仰的，\\n是女神伊莉雅的意愿吧！？\\n那你为什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "德莱茨……为什么你不说话？\\n你到底在想什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "审问结束了，\\n我没有什么要说的了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "什么！？德莱茨！？\\n我还没听到你的回答！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "和你无关。\\n埃尔菲莉丝，别再插手这件事了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "异端审问官，\\n带着她回去吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你还是坚持自己那一套吗……\\n明白了，今天就到此为止。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "等等，库格尔！\\n德莱茨！我不相信你是异端！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我一定，会证明你的清白！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "守卫，别再让她靠近这里了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "啧……区区异端，还敢趾高气昂……\\n你这家伙才是，别搞什么鬼把戏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我既不会跑也不会躲……\\n即使我的信仰被视为异端也不会。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "女神伊莉雅的意愿……吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "距离异端审判\\n还有三天",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}